<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 6 (2,300 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Trampling Charge.</em></strong> If the mammoth moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a creature and then hits it with a gore attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 18 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the mammoth can make one stomp attack against it as a bonus action.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Gore.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +10 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 25 (4d8 + 7) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Stomp.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +10 to hit, reach 5 ft., one prone creature. Hit: 29 (4d10 + 7) bludgeoning damage.</p>

